name: Dreda
content:
Dreda was a Human female smuggler fence who operated out of a mercenary camp on the Forest Moon of Endor during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Dreda was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Dreda was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
